    "Wang et al (2021a) incorporate document networks in a NTM and jointly reconstruct documents and networks.",
    "(15) = W ⊤ T.",
    "Page 11 of 30 18",
    "In addition to traditional BoW as inputs, several NTMs use graph neural networks to model documents.",
